response.overview: Follow the Nebraska Huskers behind the scenes as they prepare to "Finish Business" at the 1995 Orange Bowl. This exclusive video will take you through the Huskers' weeks of preparation and includes approximately 25 minutes of game highlights as Coach Tom Osborne's Huskers defeat the Miami Hurricanes on their own turf for the national title. You 99 will be privy to pregame and halftime speeches and will see first-hand how Osborne directs Nebraska to a 24-17 come-from-behind victory. Then follow the Huskers into the winning locker room and back to Lincoln as the Big Red Celebration continues. This 60-minute video, produced exclusively by HuskerVision (a product of the University of Nebraska), contains exclusive footage, and is a must for any sports collector.
response.tagline: Nebraska's Perfect 13-0 and National Championship Season in 1994
response.title: Finished Business
